<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 01:27:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>基于血液的环状RNA用于阿尔茨海默病的早期诊断</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/blood-based-circular-rnas-for-early-diagnosis-of-alzheimers-disease</link><description>经过大型队列测试，包含 34 种血液环状 RNA 的预测模型可以预测有症状 AD 的进展，其表现优于 pTau217 和淀粉样蛋白-PET。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/blood-based-circular-rnas-for-early-diagnosis-of-alzheimers-disease.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 01:27:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/blood-based-circular-rnas-for-early-diagnosis-of-alzheimers-disease</guid></item><item><title>科学家刚刚测量了未来计算机芯片可能的最小接触点</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-just-measured-the-smallest-possible-contacts-for-future-computer-chips</link><description>人工智能的兴起引发了人们对计算能力几乎无法满足的需求。训练和运行人工智能系统需要大量晶体管，工程师现在正在竞相将更多晶体管封装到每个芯片上。然而，根据现有的设计，硅晶体管正在迅速达到其尺寸的物理极限。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-just-measured-the-smallest-possible-contacts-for-future-computer-chips.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 01:12:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-just-measured-the-smallest-possible-contacts-for-future-computer-chips</guid></item><item><title>科学家发现防御太阳风暴的新方法以帮助保护地球</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-discover-new-method-of-defense-against-solar-storms-to-help-protect-earth</link><description>最近的一项研究揭示了我们如何应对地磁风暴，并提供了一种降低其严重程度的方法。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-discover-new-method-of-defense-against-solar-storms-to-help-protect-earth.gif" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:57:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-discover-new-method-of-defense-against-solar-storms-to-help-protect-earth</guid></item><item><title>科学家将地球的无线电波转化为音乐。聆听闪电和太阳风暴发出的怪异声音</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-turned-earths-radio-waves-into-music-listen-to-the-eerie-sounds-made-by-lightning-and-solar-storms</link><description>闪电、极光和极地风成为一张令人毛骨悚然的行星声音专辑。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-turned-earths-radio-waves-into-music-listen-to-the-eerie-sounds-made-by-lightning-and-solar-storms.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:42:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-turned-earths-radio-waves-into-music-listen-to-the-eerie-sounds-made-by-lightning-and-solar-storms</guid></item><item><title>芝加哥大学证实量子已达到晶体管时刻？——经典计算现在是 1947 年</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/university-of-chicago-confirmed-quantum-reach-its-transistor-moment-classical-computing-is-now-1947</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:27:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/university-of-chicago-confirmed-quantum-reach-its-transistor-moment-classical-computing-is-now-1947</guid></item><item><title>肠道微生物群可以在 2 型糖尿病发生前数年预测其风险</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/gut-microbiota-can-predict-risk-of-type-2-diabetes-years-before-it-develops</link><description>肠道微生物群中某些细菌的存在以及人的新陈代谢的波动可以在几年后继续患上 2 型糖尿病的人身上看到。查尔姆斯理工大学研究人员领导的一项大型瑞典研究表明了这一点。该研究是&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/gut-microbiota-can-predict-risk-of-type-2-diabetes-years-before-it-develops2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:12:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/gut-microbiota-can-predict-risk-of-type-2-diabetes-years-before-it-develops</guid></item><item><title>詹姆斯韦伯太空望远镜发现了早期宇宙中最遥远的候选棒状星系</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/jwst-finds-the-most-distant-barred-galaxy-candidate-in-the-early-universe</link><description>天文学家使用詹姆斯·韦伯太空望远镜发现了可能是迄今为止发现的最遥远的棒旋星系，其历史可以追溯到大爆炸后不到 12 亿年。概述其属性的论文已发布到&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/jwst-finds-the-most-distant-barred-galaxy-candidate-in-the-early-universe2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 23:57:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/jwst-finds-the-most-distant-barred-galaxy-candidate-in-the-early-universe</guid></item><item><title>轻度心脏问题会引发长期记忆丧失</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/mild-cardiac-issues-trigger-long-term-memory-loss</link><description>一项新的研究表明，轻微的亚临床心脏功能障碍预示着阿尔茨海默氏症大脑区域的微观组织退化。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/mild-cardiac-issues-trigger-long-term-memory-loss2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 23:42:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/mild-cardiac-issues-trigger-long-term-memory-loss</guid></item><item><title>可编程超表面一次生成数十个全息图</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/programmable-metasurface-generates-dozens-of-holograms-at-once</link><description>在过去的几十年里，工程师们开发了各种设备，可以通过精确控制行进光波的形状和方向来创建全息图、三维 (3D) 或二维 (2D) 图像。全息图现在广泛用于生成对象的视觉表示并测量其物理属性、验证文档或银行卡，并在某些教育环境中用作可视化工具。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/programmable-metasurface-generates-dozens-of-holograms-at-once2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 23:27:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/programmable-metasurface-generates-dozens-of-holograms-at-once</guid></item><item><title>钙信号传导失调是唐氏综合症唾液分泌不足和微生物失调的基础</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/dysregulated-calcium-signaling-underlies-hyposalivation-and-microbial-dysbiosis-in-down-syndrome</link><description>患有唐氏综合症（DS）的人唾液流量减少，牙周疾病负担高。在 DS 模型 Dp16 小鼠中，Son 等人。研究表明，唾液腺中钙信号传导不足是唾液分泌不足的基础，并与口腔和肠道微生物失调以及琥珀酸水平改变有关。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/dysregulated-calcium-signaling-underlies-hyposalivation-and-microbial-dysbiosis-in-down-syndrome2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 14:03:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/dysregulated-calcium-signaling-underlies-hyposalivation-and-microbial-dysbiosis-in-down-syndrome</guid></item></channel></rss>